            <title>[LU-13740] Ubuntu 20.04 LTS release</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13740</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The next LTS release of Ubuntu is now available. It includes ZFS by default and runs a 5.4 kernel. This ticket will track all the work needed to support this platform. With much of the upstreaming work this requires very little effort.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
